This paper focuses on the optimization of LiDAR configuration for self-driving cars, which falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the perception model of LiDAR, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed approach also involves optimization techniques, which can be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY).
